# Keep LF in the working tree on every OS. Without this, Windows checkouts get
# CRLF (core.autocrlf=true), which Prettier rejects — so `next build` failed
# with "Delete ␍" on every file right after a clean pull.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binaries must never be line-ending converted.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.mp3 binary
*.mp4 binary
*.wav binary
